   6:src/main.c    ****  *   1. HAL_Init → SystemClock_Config → SysTick re-init
   7:src/main.c    ****  *   2. GPIO, Timer, Comm init
   8:src/main.c    ****  *   3. Send device heartbeat
   9:src/main.c    ****  *   4. Enter main loop → process incoming protocol frames
  10:src/main.c    ****  *
